    "en": {
      "title": "Somali forces killed 40 al-Shabaab terrorists",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to foreign reports, the Somali National Army has killed at least 40 al-Shabaab terrorists while carrying out military operations in the Middle Shabelle region.",
        "Al-Shabaab is a Somalia-based extremist organization linked to al-Qaeda, and in recent years, it has launched several terrorist attacks in Somalia and its neighboring countries.",
        "Especially known as an Islamic extremist terrorist organization, cases of killing ordinary civilians and abducting children and women were also reported from time to time."
      ],
